      "message": "kernel: add `btck_set_mock_time` for testing time-dependent paths\n\nSome kernel paths read the current time (e.g. header validation's future-time check, and the `btck_SynchronizationState` carried by `btck_NotifyBlockTip` / `btck_NotifyHeaderTip` callbacks), which makes them awkward to exercise deterministically in tests. This commit exposes `btck_set_mock_time` as a wrapper over the existing `SetMockTime`, mirroring what the node has via the `setmocktime` RPC.",
